Jerry Tucker (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jerry_Tucker_(actor) 0 Jerry Tucker (November 1, 1925 – November 23, 2016) was an American child actor, most notable for having played the "rich kid" in the Our Gang short subjects series semi-regularly from 1931 to 1938.
